Entry.JapaneseText: ガジュマの人たちの視線が なんとなく冷たいんですけど？
Entry.EnglishText: Does anyone else feel like the Gajuma are giving us dirty looks?

Entry.JapaneseText: ガジュマだけではなく、ヒューマも同じような目を 俺たちに向けているぞ。
Entry.EnglishText: Not just the Gajuma, the Huma are looking at us in the same way.

Entry.JapaneseText: ヒューマとガジュマが一緒にいるのが 気に入らないみたいね。
Entry.EnglishText: It looks like they're not fans of Huma and Gajuma being around each other.
